<p>GhanaWorld's 40+ analytical cycles have scored and ranked agricultural sub-sectors based on seven dimensions: market size, infrastructure compatibility, execution feasibility, currency risk, competitive dynamics, regulatory environment, and capital efficiency. The overall Agro-Processing sector scores 8.5/10, the highest of any sector tracked.</p>

